--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

			Ziyao's TOTP Token Generator

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

= Introduction

This is a pure-C TOTP token generator modified from fmount's c_otp.

= Build

You need

 o A C99-compatible compiler
 o GNU Make

to build this program.

Running

	make

in the top directory of the repository does the build.

= Usage

	zotp <OPTIONS>

== OPTIONS

 o -h: Print the help
 o -k <secret>: Use <secret> to generate a TOTP token. ***THIS IS NOT DANGEROUS
   AS THE SECRET MAY BE STORED IN YOUR COMMAND HISTORY.***
 o -f <secret>: Load secret from <file> then generate a TOTP token. Use - for
   file to make zotp read secret from stdin.
 o -v: Print Git hash

